				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/32.9?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">2&nbsp;Nephi 32:9</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.12?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">33:12</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.23,30?lang=eng#22" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3&nbsp;Nephi 18:23, 30</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.6-7?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">19:6&ndash;7</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.31?lang=eng#30" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">20:31</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.30?lang=eng#29" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">28:30</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote29-04205_000_018">29.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/19.20-22?lang=eng#19" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3&nbsp;Nephi 19:20&ndash;22</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote30-04205_000_018">30.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/john/10.27-28?lang=eng#26" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">John 10:27&ndash;28</a> (compare <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.43-47?lang=eng#42" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 84:43&ndash;47</a>); <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.17-20?lang=eng#16" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">2&nbsp;Nephi 31:17&ndash;20</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.38?lang=eng#37" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Alma 5:38</a>. And we may invite the companionship of the Spirit, who will intercede and help us know what to pray about (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rom/8.26?lang=eng#25" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Romans 8:26</a>).</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote31-04205_000_018">31.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/25.12?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 25:12</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote32-04205_000_018">32.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/acts/14.23?lang=eng#22" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Acts 14:23</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/1-cor/7.5?lang=eng#4" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">1&nbsp;Corinthians 7:5</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/omni/1.26?lang=eng#25" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Omni 1:26</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.46?lang=eng#45" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Alma 5:46</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.6?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">6:6</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.3?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">17:3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.9?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">17:9</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/28.6?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">28:6</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/45.1?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">45:1</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.1?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3&nbsp;Nephi 27:1</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/4-ne/1.12?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">4&nbsp;Nephi 1:12</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.5?lang=eng#4" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moroni 6:5</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote33-04205_000_018">33.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.76?lang=eng#75" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 88:76</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote34-04205_000_018">34.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Joseph&nbsp;F. Smith, in Conference Report, Oct. 1912, 133&ndash;34.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote35-04205_000_018">35.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Joseph Smith Translation, Psalm 17:1.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote36-04205_000_018">36.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See Spencer&nbsp;W. Kimball, <span class="emphasis">Faith Precedes the Miracle </span>(1972), 201; Stephen&nbsp;L Richards, in Conference Report, Oct. 1951, 175; Bruce&nbsp;R. McConkie, &ldquo;Why the Lord Ordained Prayer,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> Jan. 1976, 12; L.&nbsp;Tom Perry, &ldquo;Our Father Which Art in Heaven,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> Nov. 1983, 13; and Dallin&nbsp;H. Oaks, &ldquo;The Language of Prayer,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> May 1993, 15&ndash;18. Details of that language are explained by Don&nbsp;E. Norton Jr., &ldquo;The Language of Formal Prayer,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> Jan. 1976, 44&ndash;47.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote37-04205_000_018">37.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/112.10?lang=eng#9" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 112:10</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/ot/ps/24.3-4?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Psalm 24:3&ndash;4</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/matt/6.12?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Matthew 6:12</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/hel/3.35?lang=eng#34" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Helaman 3:35</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.8-10?lang=eng#7" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 64:8&ndash;10</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote38-04205_000_018">38.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rev/3.20?lang=eng#19" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Revelation 3:20</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote39-04205_000_018">39.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.20?lang=eng#19" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3&nbsp;Nephi 18:20</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.64?lang=eng#63" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 88:64</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote40-04205_000_018">40.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.37?lang=eng#36" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Alma 37:37</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/philip/4.6?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Philippians 4:6</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.18-27?lang=eng#17" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Alma 34:18&ndash;27</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.5?lang=eng#4" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 10:5</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.49?lang=eng#48" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">93:49</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote41-04205_000_018">41.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.1?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3&nbsp;Nephi 20:1</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote42-04205_000_018">42.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <span class="emphasis">Ensign, </span>Jan. 1976, 11.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote43-04205_000_018">43.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Thomas&nbsp;S. Monson, &ldquo;A Royal Priesthood,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Liahona </span>and <span class="emphasis">Ensign,</span> Nov. 2007, 61.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote44-04205_000_018">44.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/matt/26.42?lang=eng#41" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Matthew 26:42</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/jacob/7.14?lang=eng#13" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Jacob 7:14</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.29?lang=eng#28" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Ether 12:29</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.44?lang=eng#43" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 109:44</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.2?lang=eng#1" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 4:2</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote45-04205_000_018">45.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.13-15,21-22?lang=eng#12" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">3&nbsp;Nephi 27:13&ndash;15, 21&ndash;22</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote46-04205_000_018">46.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.7?lang=eng#6" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Mosiah 15:7</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote47-04205_000_018">47.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/matt/26.39?lang=eng#38" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Matthew 26:39</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.2?lang=eng#1" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 4:2</a>, which indicates the humble attitude of our Savior from the beginning.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-04205_000_018"><a name="-04205_000_018">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote48-04205_000_018">48.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/65.5?lang=eng#4" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 65:5</a>.</p>
			</li>
		</ol>
                                        
